The '''Accademia di belle arti di Reggio Calabria''' is an academy of fine arts located in [[Reggio Calabria]], Italy. It was founded in 1967.<ref>{{cite book|last1=Giovanna Cassese|title= Accademie Patrimoni di Belle Arti|publisher=Gangemi, 2013|isbn=8849276710}}</ref>

