====1965–1969==== ''Shōnen Book'' announces more series. A video game of ''[[Obake no Q-tarō]]'' was released in the States as ''[[Chubby Cherub]]''. ''Shōnen Book'' closed, and was replaced with the offshoot: ''Bessatsu Shōnen Jump''.
